                  Chirag Shah and
                  Torsten Suel and
                  Pablo Castells and
                  Rosie Jones and
                  Tetsuya Sakai},
	title = {{SDG:} {A} Simplified and Dynamic Graph Neural Network},
	booktitle = {{SIGIR} '21: The 44th International {ACM} {SIGIR} Conference on Research
